# AutoGuide

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) before changing code.

## Stack

- pnpm monorepo: `packages/`, `plugins/`, `examples/`, `integrations/`
- TypeScript strict; `@autoguide/core` stays framework-agnostic
- UI/errors Deutsch; commits and PR text English
- Quality gate: `pnpm run verify`

## Workflow

- Issue branches only — never commit directly to `main`
- Acceptance: `.qa/acceptance/<slug>.md` when present
- Ship only after `@ecc-check` READY
